FBIS3-26969 "drchi033_a_94012" FBIS-CHI-94-033 Document Type:Daily Report 17 February 1994 INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS General Foreign Ministry Spokesman Announces Visits Italian Senate President To Visit OW1702084394 Beijing XINHUA in English 0831 GMT 17 Feb 94 OW1702084394 Beijing XINHUA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Beijing, February 17 (XINHUA) -- Giovanni Spatolini, president of the Senate of Italy will pay a goodwill visit to China from February 18 to 23 at the invitation of the Standing Committee of China's National People's Congress. This was announced by a spokesman of the Chinese Foreign Ministry at a weekly press conference here this afternoon.
